 ==============================================================================
 use the function in this folder:
 
 import pencilnew as pcn
 pcn.mycode.*functionname*
 
 """
 make sure the file pencilnew/__init__.py has the following words:
     'from . import mycode  	     # functions in mycode directory'
 """
 ==============================================================================

 ==============================================================================
 if you want to add a function in this folder:
 
 1. add the .py file in this folder
 2. rewrite the __init__.py file which locates in this folder to 
         import your function like other functions 
 3. make sure the file pencilnew/__init__.py has the following codes:
     'from . import mycode  	     # functions in mycode directory'
 ==============================================================================
